description:
THERE IS SOMETHING I WANT FROM YOU…

Is there a more terrifying thought than, one day your wife will just get tired of you and divorce you without out a second thought taking half of everything and leave your life in tatters?  There actually is something worse than that.  What if one evening you wake up and can’t move?   What if your wife has done something that could make your heart explode?  What if she makes you sign life insurance papers, and you are unable to resist doing so?
title: PUTTING DOWN HER HUSBAND… AND COLLECTING THE LOOT
